<template>
  <gucp-dialog ref="userDialog" :title="$t('addUser')" :confirm-label="$t('create')"
    @confirm="onConfirmCreateType('createForm')">
    <el-form ref="createForm" :model="createForm" label-suffix=":" label-position="left" label-width="90px">
      <el-form-item :label="$t('account')" prop="Account">
        <el-input v-model="createForm.username" />
      </el-form-item>
      <el-form-item :label="$t('passWord')" prop="Password">
        <el-input v-model="createForm.password" type="password" />
      </el-form-item>
      <el-form-item :label="$t('email')" prop="Email">
        <el-input v-model="createForm.email" type="email" />
      </el-form-item>
      <el-form-item :label="$t('nickName')" prop="Nickname">
        <el-input v-model="createForm.nickname" />
      </el-form-item>
      <el-form-item :label="$t('realName')" prop="Realname">
        <el-input v-model="createForm.realname" />
      </el-form-item>
      <el-form-item :label="$t('tel')" prop="Tel">
        <el-input v-model="createForm.phone" />
      </el-form-item>
    </el-form>
  </gucp-dialog>
</template>
<script>
export default {
  data () {
    return {
      createForm: {
        username: '',
        password: '',
        email: '',
        nickname: '',
        realname: '',
        phone: ''
      }
    }
  },
  methods: {
    open () {
      this.$refs.userDialog.open()
      this.createForm = {
        username: '',
        password: '',
        email: '',
        nickname: '',
        realname: '',
        phone: ''
      }
    },
    onConfirmCreateType (formName) {
      this.$refs[formName].validate(valid => {
        if (valid) {
          if (!this.createForm.username) {
            this.$message.error(this.$t('AccountNoEmpty'))
            return false
          } else if (!this.createForm.password) {
            this.$message.error(this.$t('PasswordNoEmpty'))
            return false
          } else if (!this.createForm.email) {
            this.$message.error(this.$t('EmailNoEmpty'))
            return false
          } else if (!this.createForm.nickname) {
            this.$message.error(this.$t('NicknameNoEmpty'))
            return false
          } else if (!this.createForm.phone) {
            this.$message.error(this.$t('PhoneNoEmpty'))
            return false
          }
          this.$emit('success', { data: this.createForm, code: 0 })
          this.$refs.userDialog.close()
        } else {
          return false
        }
      })
    }
  }
}
</script>
